See "Orthogonal-Normalize U2 normalize w2 (-0.707, 0.707) = "  MatrixPrint(U2)

U3 =  ScalarMultiply( (1/VectorNorm(w3)), w3 )
See "Orthogonal-Normalize U3 normalize w2 (0,0,1) = "  MatrixPrint(U3)


